## Management Commands

```bash
# Start/Stop/Restart service
systemctl start invsys
systemctl stop invsys
systemctl restart invsys

# View logs
tail -f /root/invsys/logs/gunicorn-error.log
tail -f /var/log/nginx/invsys_error.log

# Generate test data
python manage.py populate_test_data --customers 60 --quotations 100 --invoices 150 --clear

# Generate receivables report
python manage.py receivables_report

# Collect static files
python manage.py collectstatic --noinput
```

